cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DC, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it deals with training large neural networks and optimization techniques. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves improving the efficiency of machine learning algorithms. Additionally, since the paper uses deep Imagenet models, it could be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also discusses distributed optimization, which could place it under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
